      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁婆上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我做禁婆管牢囚，十人见了九人愁。有钱的好应酬，无钱的打不罢来骂不休，"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕旁人作对头，作对头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我乃山阳县内禁婆是也。只因窦娥来到我这监中，也有好些日子，一个钱也不"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿出来。今日把她叫出来，有钱便罢；要是无钱，打她两下，也好出出我这点"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "气吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说窦娥，窦娥，与我滚出来罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "苦吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦娥上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说是唤窦娥愁锁眉上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "唬得我战兢兢无处躲藏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "滚出来罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "又见她发了怒有话难讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "禁妈妈呼唤我所为哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妈妈在上，窦娥有礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有礼，我倒没有礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，妈妈唤奴出来。有何话讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦蛾，我来问你：你到我这监中，日子也不少了。又道是：靠山吃山，靠水吃"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "水。你倒有钱拿点出来，妈妈也好垫补垫补。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，妈妈说哪里话来。想我窦娥遭此不白冤枉，家业如同水洗一股，哪有银钱"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与妈妈使用？望妈妈行个方便罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来一个行方便。来两个行方便。叫妈妈吃什么鸡巴根子？你这来，有何人话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "照打罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁婆打窦娥。窦娥哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听罢言来怒气生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由老身咬牙根。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦娥哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "活活打死你这小贱人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦娥 （哭板） 我哭、哭一声禁妈妈，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫、叫、叫、叫一声禁大娘："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家业一旦化费光。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "求望妈妈行善良，呵呵呵我那好心的人哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁婆哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，妈妈是铁嘴豆腐心，见不得这个样的人。你起来你起来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢妈妈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说你一来有冤枉，两来有冤枉。你把你的冤枉说出来，妈妈听一听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妈妈吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐下慢慢说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "禁妈妈你请上容奴细讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "都只为我婆婆染病在床。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "买羊肚下毒药起下不良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "那一日他的母也在一旁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他的母吃羊肚命丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "张驴儿仗男子说话强梁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "就将我窦娥女问罪抵偿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "无情棍棒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "要明冤除非是包公还阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有谁知张驴儿天良尽丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老天爷岂容那贼子妄想"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这也是我婆婆命不该丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "实指望到公堂辩明冤枉"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "县太爷他也不明查暗访"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不招认受不过"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好了不要哭了，你歇歇罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡母上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叹媳妇遭下了不白寃枉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倒叫我年迈人好不惨伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，禁大娘，开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可是坐监的来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是呵，我是窦娥的婆婆，前来探望于她。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，你是窦娥的婆婆来看他。好好好，拿来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿什么来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的规矩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，禁大娘，我乃贫寒人家，哪有银钱侍奉？大娘行个方便罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，又是行方便。不行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老身跪下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎唷哎唷，怎么又遇见这个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起来起来，我来开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳妈妈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡母进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "媳妇儿在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要嚷，你随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦娥吓，你婆婆来看你来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婆婆在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蔡母 （同叫头） （婆婆）（儿吓）！（母亲）（媳妇）！哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦娥、蔡母同哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见媳妇不像人模样，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倒叫我年迈人痛断肝肠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，婆婆到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为婆带来水饭，与我儿充饥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿吞吃不下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少用些。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来，我先看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妈妈请看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，没什么，吃罢"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！快叫吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "媳妇醒来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一口气噎得我咽喉哑尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婆婆！大娘！哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "险些儿婆媳们两下离分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禁妈妈，我儿吞吃不下，取碗凉水来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我去取水去，你们好好的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁婆下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳妈妈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看我儿青丝散乱，待为婆与你梳洗梳洗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳婆婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝姣儿休得要泪流满面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝媳妇休悲痛切莫惨伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨张驴他不该丧尽天良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那时节婆媳们回家去，满斗焚香，答谢上苍，我那窦娥儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "遭不幸遇下了不白冤枉"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若是遇清官将儿来放"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老婆婆休把那宽心话讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "看起来也是儿命该早亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再不想与婆婆熬药煎汤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "再不想早晚间侍举高堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要相逢除非是梦里一场。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁婆上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦娥，大事不好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥、蔡母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "京详已到：明日午时三刻，就要将你斩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你但怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就要斩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁婆、蔡母",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "窦娥醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言唬得我三魂飘荡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "婆婆！大娘！哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "窦娥",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那贼子他害我一命身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说大娘一声讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡母",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "婆媳就要两分张。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（窦娥、蔡母同哭，同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "窦娥→禁婆",
          "turns": 11
